                    <span>If you're planning on doing some business in China and are unfamiliar with Chinese customs- do yourself a favor and read this book. Concise, well written and informative, Chinese Business Etiquette is a good introduction to getting by in the Middle Kingdom.<P>Besides helping you to do business in China, this book can also prevent you from looking like a complete moron in a Chinese social situation.</span>
                  
              
